{"tid":1366514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4元朗居民提交元朗遊行新路線申請","createTime":"2019-07-26T03:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:50:08.000Z","uid":212626,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff08b57f185ff581bd662c32570cc2dcf04a31d","tid":1366514,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"警方向計劃在周六發起「光復元朗」遊行的申請人鍾健平發出反對遊行及禁止集會通知後，4名元朗居民今早到元朗警署提交新申請，提出將遊行路線改為元朗天后誕巡遊路線，由元朗西鐵站至朗屏西鐵站，不會途經大馬路及鄉村。<br />\n<br />\n他們相信，新方案可以改善原申請人因遊行路線令申請被拒的問題，但對成功獲得警方發出不反對通知書的信心仍然不大；又指預計遊行人數為5萬人，將安排30名糾察維持秩序。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2201233/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2201233%2F&d=AixoiqhHuTrv0%2F0Xa%2FX9xwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=9b5e460d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2201233/</a>"},{"pid":"86119812856cc6f2643700d1c18794559acedac1","tid":1366514,"uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但對成功獲得警方發出不反對通知書的信心仍然不大</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1645747c7fef45ab551a444a42f10e9b06cc0e7","tid":1366514,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"86119812856cc6f2643700d1c18794559acedac1","tid":1366514,"uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但對成功獲得警方發出不反對通知書的信心仍然不大</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"唔reject就OK"},{"pid":"7cd871ad520bf1458c5fc11fe4044d8b64bab4a7","tid":1366514,"uid":200328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"又指預計遊行人數為5萬人<br />\n<br />\n只唔只啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db520821fa9b5c978c151d4630